Document: VisualShaderNodeCubemapParameter
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodecubemapparameter.rst
Summary: Class representing a cubemap parameter node in a visual shader. Inherits from VisualShaderNodeParameter and is used to sample cubemap textures in shader graphs.
