Document: VisualShaderNodeCubeMapParameter
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodecubemapparameter.rst
Summary: Represents a cube map parameter in visual shaders, translated to uniform samplerCube and compatible with VisualShaderNodeCubemap.

Translated to uniform samplerCube in the shader language. The output value can be used as port for VisualShaderNodeCubemap.